eal estate and multifamily loans its corporate and commercial banking segment offers commercial loans and commercial deposits financing and deposits for government entities and niche product financing for specific industries including oil and gas mortgage warehousing and other industries the company’s global corporate banking segment provides financing and banking services to commercial and institutional customers it offers auto financing products and services including retail installment contracts and leases as well as dealer loans for inventory construction real estate working capital and revolving lines of credit to chrysler customers and dealers under the chrysler capital brand and originates vehicle loans through a webbased direct lending program purchases vehicle rics from other lenders and services automobile recreational and marine vehicle portfolios for other lenders as of december   it had  branches and  automated teller machines the company was founded in  and is headquartered in boston massachusetts santander holdings usa inc is a subsidiary of banco santander sa detailed description  state streetboston ma united statesfounded in  phone  wwwsantanderbankcom key executives for santander holdings usa inc mr scott e powell chief executive officer president and director age  mr madhukar dayal chief financial officer and senior executive vice president age  mr julio somoza managing director of technology  operations and senior executive vice president age  mr alvaro morales chief executive officer of banco santander international mr fredy molfino ceo of banco santander puerto rico and ceo of santander bancorp compensation as of fiscal year  santander holdings usa inc key developments santander holdings usa inc announces the completion and final results of its tender offer and all of its  senior notes due  jul   santander holdings usa inc announced the completion and final results of its previously announced cash tender offer for any and all of its outstanding